law.text:
The board shall:
Administer and enforce the provisions of KRS 323.400 to 323.416 and 323.992;
Maintain an official roster of all certified interior designers;
Require a certified interior designer to include the certified interior designer's certificate number on all business and advertising documents;
Review all applications of persons applying for certification under KRS 323.400 to 323.416 and 323.992 and approve the certification of those persons who meet the requirements of a certified interior designer.
